  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to (1) compare the efficacy of the BEACOPP regimen with that of ABVD
      as a 4-cycle chemotherapy combined with an involved field irradiation and (2) to define the
      optimum radiation dose comparing of 30 to 20 Gy in the same context.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
